# IMPORTANT: do NOT ignore dist/ — we commit it because jsdelivr serves
# directly from the GitHub repo path. The Shopify Page <script src="...">
# URL points at dist/assets/index.js, so the built artifacts MUST be in
# the repo for the CDN to serve them.
